                  <join result="persNameOccupation" targOrder="Y" targets="t18270531-232-victim1289 t18270531-232-viclabel1239"></join>, and live in Holborn. The prisoner was about three weeks in my employ - I gave him 18 shillings to take to St. John's-square, to buy some books at Mr. Dove's.</p>
